Class MslCiphertextEnvelope

java.lang.Object
  com.netflix.msl.crypto.MslCiphertextEnvelope

public class MslCiphertextEnvelope
extends Object

MSL ciphertext envelopes contain all of the information necessary for decrypting ciphertext using a known key.
